    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">友</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>まじ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">今日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よりは<lb />
ねたまじ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">君</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">濃藍</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">のうらん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">底見</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そこみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>えわかぬわたづみの<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">珊瑚</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さんご</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">宮</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">得</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">え</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>て<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">幸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くあり、とに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">止</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">や</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>まむ。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">濃藍</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こあゐ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たゞえて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">見</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>えわかぬ<lb />
わたづみ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">底</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぞこ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なれば<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">誰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">た</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">子</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">誰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">た</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">子</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">手</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">て</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をとりて<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">口</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>つけかはし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">笑</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゑ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みかはし<lb />
ありともいかで<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">名</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">知</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>らむ。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はれぬ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">嫉妬</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ねたみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>もて、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">相合</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あひあ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ふ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">魂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">咀</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">のろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ふとも、<lb />
三<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">月</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぐわつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">尽</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">百蓮華</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">びやくれんげ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">得</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">え</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>やは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">枯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">から</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さむあたゝかき<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">蕾</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つぼみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ふくめる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">緋牡丹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひぼたん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寄藻</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よりも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">匂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">にほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はざる。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">荒磯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ありそ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">辺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">照</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">て</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">晒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>らされて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">帆立貝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほたてがい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">帆</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">失</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なひぬ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">砂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">上</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">へ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">歯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">は</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をくひあてゝ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">滅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ばゞや<lb />
<lb />
とおもひにしも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">怨疾</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">をんしつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">膿</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">悩</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>める<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">昨夜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よべ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なりし、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">帆</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">失</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なひし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">貝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ならば<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">今日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>より<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">安</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やす</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>からむ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">荒磯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ありそ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">上</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>や<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寂光土</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じやくくわうど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>――<lb />
<lb />
ねたみくづれし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ならば<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">今日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よりなげきあらためむ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">法</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">のり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">雨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">降</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れあゝさらば、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">乱</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みだ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">飛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>びし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">花片</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はなびら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">濡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぬ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">朽</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">く</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たしめよ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">土着</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つちき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>せよ。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">日毎</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひごと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夜毎</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よごと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にかはり<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にかはりてもあゝ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">友</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ<lb />
ねたまじ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">友</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">恋人</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こひゞと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ、<lb />
こひねがはくは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">円</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かなる<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">愛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">光</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">仰</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がしめずや。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
